hadiths[183]{hadithnumber,text}:
2437,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jab Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen ki taraf (muballigh aur haakim bana kar) bheja to un sey farmaya : to wahan ehle-kitab (yahudiyon) key paas ja raha hai. jab to unkey paas pahunchey to in ko is baat ki dawat dena ke wo gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool o peghambar hain. agar wo teri is baat ko maan lein to unhein batana ke Allah ney un par har din aur raat mein paanch namazein farz ki hain. agar wo teri is baat ko maan le to in ko batana ke Allah ney un par Zakat farz ki hai jo unkey maal-daar logon sey ley kar unhi key mohtaj logon mein taqseem kar di jaeygi. agar wo teri ye baat taslim kar len to (zakaat ki wasuli aur deegar intizami maamlat mein) mazloom ki badduaa sey bachna.
2438,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mainey (Islam latey waqt) kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! mainey yahan aap key paas aaney sey pehley apney haathon ki ungliyon ki tadaad (yani das) sey bhi ziyada dafa qism khai thi ke main na aap key paas aaunga aur na aap ka Deen qubul karunga. (lekin Allah Taala ney mujhey hidayat di hai to hazir ho gaya hun). main be-samajh aadmi hun. mujhey kuchh malum nahin magar jo Allah aur us ka Rasool mujhey sikhaeingey. main Allah Taala ki ""wahi"" key wastey sey aap sey sawal karta hun ke Allah Taala ney aap ko kya dey kar hamari taraf bheja hai? aap ney farmaya : Islam dey kar. mainey arz kya : Islam ki khas baaten kya hain? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to kahe : mainey apni zaat ko Allah Taala key ehkamaat key liye muteea' kar diya hai aur main har qism key shirk sey laa-taaluq ho gaya hun. aur to namaz (ba-jamaat) padhey aur Zakat ki adaegi kerey."
2439,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : achchhi tarah wuzu karna nisf (aadha) eman hai. « Alhamdulillah » kehna meezaan (tarazu) ko bhar deta hai. « Subhan Allah » aur « Allahu-Akbar » kehna aasman aur zamin ko bhar detey hain. namaz Noor hai, Zakat (emaan ki) daleel hai, sabr roshni hai aur Quran Majeed hujjat hai terey haq mein ya terey khilaf ."
2440,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik din hamein khutba irshad farmatey huye teen dafa farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai !. phir aap ney sar jhuka liya. hum mein sey har shakhs bhi sar jhuka kar roney laga. hum nahin jantey they ke aap ney kis chiz par qism khai hai? phir aap ney sar mubarak uthaya to chehrey mein khushi key aasaar they aur aap ki khushi hamarey liye surkh oonton sey bhi ziyada mehbub thi, phir aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs paanch farz namazen padhey aur Ramzan key rozey rakhey, Zakat ada karey aur saat kabeera gunahon sey perhez kerey. uskey liye jannat key sab darwazey khol diye jaeyngey aur usey kaha jaeyga : salamti key sath jannat mein dakhil ho ja."
2441,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs kisi chiz ka joda Allah Taala key raastey mein kharch kerey. usey jannat key darwazon sey pukara jaeyga, aey Allah key bandey ! ye (darwaza) terey liye behtar hai. aur jannat key bahut sey darwazey hain. jo shakhs namaz ka aadi hoga, usey namaz waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga aur jo jihad ka shauqeen tha, usey jihad waley darwazey sey aawaz di jaeygi aur jo sadqey sey khususi raghbat rakhney wala hoga, usey sadqey waley darwazey sey dawat di jaeygi aur jo rozey ka rasiyaa hoga, usey baabul-Rayyaan sey dakhil honey ko kaha jaeyga. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : kisi shakhs ko koi zarurat to nahin ke usey un sab darwazon sey bulaya jaey magar kya koi aisa shakhs bhi hoga jisey un sab darwazon sey aawazen di jaeyngi? aap ney farmaya : haan, aur mujhey ummid hai, aey Abu-Bakar ! tum unhi mein sey hogey."
2442,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aap Kaabey key saye mein bethey they. jab aap ney mujhey aatey dekha to farmaney lagey : Kaabey key Rab ki qism ! wo bahut khasarey (nuksaan) waley log hain. mainey apney dil mein kaha : kya wajeh hai? shayad merey barey mein koi ""wahi"" utri hai. mainey arz kiya : aap par merey maa baap qurban ! wo kon (bad-naseeb) hain? aap ney farmaya : ziyada maaldaar log, magar jisney aisey, aisey aur aisey kiya. yani aagey, apney daeyn aur baain kharch kiya, phir farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! jo aadmi bhi martey waqt oont aur gaayen chhod jaaey, jin ki Zakat wo na deta ho, uskey janwer us jasaamat aur motaapey sey badh kar aayengey jo (duniya mein) thi aur usey apney paon taley rondengey aur usko apney seengon sey takkareyn maarengey. jab un mein sey aakhiri janwer guzar jaeyga to pehley ko dobara uskey ooper sey guzaaraa jaeyga. (us key sath ye silsila jari raheyga) yahan tak ke logon key darmiyan faisley kar diye jaeyn."
2443,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ka haq (zakaat) ada na karta ho to (qiyamat key din) wo maal uskey galey mein ganjey sanp ki surat mein toq bana diya jaeyga. wo us sey bhageyga, magar wo uskey peechhey daudeyga, phir aap ney Allah Taala ki kitab mein sey uski tasdeeq key liye ye aayat padhi : (وَلَا یَحْسَبَنَّ الَّذِیْنَ یَبْخَلُوْنَ … الخ), ""jo log Allah Taala key diye huye maal mein bukhl kartey hain, wo ye na samjhen ke wo maal unkey liye behtar hai, balke wo unkey liye badtar hai. aur jis maal key sath unhoney bukhl kiya, qiyamat key din wo unkey galey ka toq banaya jaeyga."
2444,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jis aadmi key paas oont hon aur wo unki (najda) aur unki (risl) mein unka haq (yani zakaat) ada na karta ho. sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (najda) aur (risl) sey kya murad hai? aap ney farmaya : tangi aur khush-haali mein (un ki Zakat ada na karta ho) to (qiyamat key din) wo intehai motey taazey aur puri masti ki haalat mein ayengey aur us (Malik) ko unkey samney eik khuley humwaar maidan mein ondha litaa diya jaeyga to wo apney khuron sey (paon taley) usey maslen (ronden) gey. jab aakhiri guzar jaeyga to pehley ko phir laya jaeyga aur ye kaam uskey sath qiyamat key purey din mein kiya jata raheyga. jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hai, yahan tak ke logon key darmiyan (jannat aur jahannam ka) faisla kar diya jaey. aur wo apna (jannat ya jahannam wala) raasta dekh ley. aur (isi tarah) jis shakhs key paas gaayen hon aur wo tang haali aur khush haali mein un ki Zakat na deta ho to wo bhi qiyamat key din intehai moti tazi aur puri masti ki haalat mein ayengi aur us (Malik) ko unkey samney eik khuley humwaar maidan mein ondha litaa diya jaeyga aur har seeng wali apney seengon sey us ko takkareyn maareygi aur har khur wali apney khuron key sath us ko kuchleygi. jab un mein sey aakhiri guzar jaeygi to pehli ko phir laya jaeyga. aur ye kaam uskey sath qiyamat key purey din mein kiya jata raheyga jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hai, yahan tak ke logon key darmiyan faisla kiya jaey aur wo apna (jannati ya jahannami) raasta dekh leyga. isi tarah jis aadmi key paas bakriyan hon aur wo tang haali aur khush-haali mein un ki Zakat na deta ho to wo qiyamat key din intehai moti tazi aur puri masti ki haalat mein ayengi, phir us (Malik) ko unkey samney eik khuley aur humwaar maidan mein ondha litaa diya jaeyga. to har khur wali apney khuron key sath usko masleygi aur har seeng wali apney seengon key sath us ko takkaren maareygi. un mein sey kisi ka seeng na muda huwa hoga aur na tootaa huwa. jab un mein sey aakhiri guzar jaeygi to pehli ko wapis laya jaeyga. aur us (Malik) key sath ye kaam qiyamat key purey din hota rahega jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hogi, yahan tak ke logon key darmiyan (jannat aur jahannam ka) faisla kar diya jaey aur wo apna (jannat ya jahannam wala) raasta dekh ley."
2445,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey aur aap key baad Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa banaey gaey aur bahut sey Arab logon ney kufr ka irtikab kiya (aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey ladney ka aelan farmaya) to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap un logon sey kaisey ladengey (jo Zakat nahin detey) jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : mujhey logon key sath ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke woh (لا الہ الا اللہ) (kalima tayiba) padh lein. jis shakhs ney (لا الہ الا اللہ) padh liya, us ney mujh sey apni jaan aur maal bacha liya siwaey iske ke is par koi haq banta ho. aur us ka (andruni) hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main un logon sey zarur ladunga jo namaz aur Zakat mein farq kerengey kyonkey Zakat maal ka haq hai. Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey (bil-farz oont ko baandhney wali) rassi na den jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main uskey na deney par bhi un sey ladunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney (baad mein) farmaya : Allah ki qism ! meri samajh mein bhi ye baat aa gaee ke ladaai key liye Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina Allah Taala ney khol diya hai to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke yehi haq hai."
2446,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha, mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : sehra mein charney waley oonton mein sey har chaalis oonton main eik binte-laboon (do saala oontni) hai. (dorane wasuli) oonton key hisab aur miqdaar sey unhein alag na kiya jaeyga. jo shakhs (khushi sey) sawab ki khatir Zakat deyga, us ko us ka sawab milega aur jo deney sey inkar kerega hum Zakat bhi leingey aur (us key sath sath) uskey nisf (aadhe) oont bhi lengey. (kyonkey) ye Zakat hamarey Rab key faraaiz mein sey eik aham fariza hai. Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key khandan key liye kuchh bhi Zakat lena (apni zaat key liye) jayez nahin."
2447,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch wasq sey kam ghalley mein Zakat nahin, na paanch sey kam oonton mein Zakat hai aur na paanch oqiye sey kam raqam mein Zakat hai."
2448,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch oonton sey kam mein Zakat nahin aur paanch oqiye sey kam (chaandi ya raqam) main Zakat nahin aur paanch wasq sey kam ghalley mein Zakat nahin."
2449,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) (khalifa Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un (zakaat ke governer) ko ye tehreer likh bheji : ye wo muqarrar shuda sadqaat hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon par muqarrar farmaai aur Allah Taala ney unka apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya. jis musalman sey ye sadqaat muqarrara tareeqae-kaar key mutabiq talab kiye jaeyn to wo laziman ada karey aur jis sey muqarrara miqdaar sey zayed maangey jaaeyn, wo na dey. (un ki tafsil ye hai : ) oont pachchees sey kam hon to har paanch oonton main eik bakri (zakaat) hai. jab oont pachchees ho jaeyn to n main eik binte makhaaz (eik baras ki oontni) hai. paintis tak yehi Zakat hogi. agar eik baras ki (mada) oontni na ho to do baras ka (nar) oont (zakaat) hai. jab wo chhattis ho jaeyn to paintaalees tak un main eik binte-labun (do baras ki oontni) hai. jab wo chhiyaalees ho jaeyn to saath (60) tak eik hiqqa (teen baras ki oontni) hai. jo nar ki jufti key qabil ho. jab iksath ho jaeyn to pachhattar tak eik jazaa (chaar baras ki mada oontni zakaat) hai. jab wo chhiyattar (76) ho jaaeyn to nawwey tak un mein do binte-laboon (do do baras ki do oontniyaan) Zakat hain. jab wo ikkyanwe ho jaeyn to eik sau bees tak do hiqqa (teen teen baras ki do oontniyaan) hain jo nar ki jufti key qabil hon. jab eik sau-bees sey zayed ho jaeyn to har chaalis main eik binte-labun aur har pachas main eik hiqqa (zakaat) hai. agar oonton ki umren mukhtalif hon (aur muqarrara umr key oont na mil saken) to jis aadmi key zimmey jazaa ho aur us ko jazaa muyassar na ho, albatta uskey paas hiqqa ho to us sey hiqqa hi li jaeygi aur uskey sath do bakriyan li jaeyngi, agar usey muyassar hon, warna bees dirham liye jaeyngey. aur jis shakhs key zimmey hiqqa Zakat ho magar uskey paas sirf jazaa hai to us sey wohi li jaeygi aur Zakat wasul karney wala us ko bees dirham ya agar muyassar hon to do bakriyan wapis kerega. isi tarah agar kisi aadmi key zimmey hiqa Zakat banti ho lekin uskey paas hiqqa na ho balke uskey paas binte-laboon ho to wohi us sey li jaeygi aur uskey sath mazeed do bakriyan li jaeyngi, agar usey muyassar hon, warna bees dirham liye jaeyngey. aur jis shakhs key zimmey binte-labun  Zakat banti ho magar uskey paas sirf hiqqa ho to us sey wohi li jaeygi aur sadqa wasul karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan wapis kerega. isi tarah jis shakhs key zimmey bint-labun Zakat banti ho, magar uskey paas binte-labun na ho balke binte-makhaaz ho to us sey wohi li jaeygi aur uskey sath mazeed do bakriyan deyga, agar usey muyassar hun, warna bees dirham deyga. aur jis aadmi key zimmey binte-makhaaz Zakat banti ho, magar uskey paas sirf ibne laboon ho to us sey wohi liya jaeyga aur uskey sath koi aur chiz na li jaeygi. aur jis aadmi key paas sirf chaar oont hon to un mein koi Zakat wajib nahin magar Malik khushi sey dena chahey (to alag baat hai). aur jangal mein charney wali bakriyan hon aur chaalis ho jaeyn to eik sau bees tak eik bakri Zakat hai. jab us sey eik bhi zayed ho jaey to do sau tak do bakriyan Zakat hai. jab us sey eik bhi badh jaey to teen sau tak teen bakriyan Zakat hai. aur jab is sey badh jaeyn to har sau main eik bakri Zakat hogi. Zakat mein boodha ya kaanaa (aeb wala) janwer ya nar bakra nahin liya jaeyga. han, agar sadqa wasul karney wala chahey to nar bakra ley sakta hai. alehda alehda janweron ko (zakaat key moqe par) ikhatta nahin kiya jaeyga, isi tarah ikhattey rehney waley janweron ko Zakat key dar sey alag alag nahin kiya jaeyga. aur jo Zakat do shareek malikon sey wasul ki jaey, wo aapas mein apney janweron key hisab sey taqseem kar leingey. aur agar jangal aur sehra mein charney wali bakriyan chaalis sey kam hon, chahey (chaahey) eik hi kam ho, un mein koi Zakat nahin magar Malik khushi sey dena chahey (to alag baat hai). aur chaandi mein chaaliswaan hissa Zakat hai lekin agar eik-sau-nawwey dirham hon (yani 200 dirham sey kam hon). to un mein koi Zakat nahin magar ye ke Malik khud dena chahey."
2450,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar oonton key Malik ney unka haq ada nahin kiya hoga (un ki Zakat na di hogi) to wo oont (qiyamat key din) behtareen motaapey ki haalat mein is par ayengey aur usey apney paon sey rondengey. aur agar bakriyon key Malik ney unka haq ada nahin kiya hoga (un ki Zakat na di hogi) to wo bakriyan (qiyamat key din) behtareen motaapey ki haalat mein is par aayengi, usey apney khuron sey maslengi aur apney seengon sey usey takkaren maarengi. farmaya : aur un janweron mein ye haq bhi hai ke jab wo pani peeney jaeyn to (wahan mojud fuqaraa ko) unka doodh doh kar diya jaey. khabrdar ! aisa na ho ke qiyamat key din tum mein sey koi shakhs apni gardan par oont uthaey huye aaye aur wo oont bulbula raha ho. wo kahe : aey Muhammad ! (meri madad farmaiye) aur main keh dun ke main terey barey mein koi ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. mainey tumhen tableegh kar di thi. khabrdar ! aisa na ho ke tum mein sey koi shakhs qiyamat key din apni gardan par bakri utha kar laye, wo bakri mimiya rahi ho aur wo kahe : aey Muhammad ! (meri madad farmaiye) aur main keh dun ke main terey barey mein koi ikhtiyar nahin rakhta. mainey tumhen tableegh kar di thi, isi ke saath aap ney farmaya : un (logon) ka khazana (jis ki Zakat na di gaee ho) qiyamat key din ganjey sanp ki surat ikhtiyar kerega. us ka Malik us sey bhageyga lekin wo usey talash kerega aur kahega : main tera khazana hun. wo isi tarah us ka peechha karta raheyga yahan tak ke wo apni ungliyan us (saanp) key munh mein dal deyga."
2451,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada ney kaha ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : bahar charney waley oonton ki Zakat har chaalis oonton main eik binte-labun (do baras ki oontni) hai. oonton ko unkey hisab aur miqdaar sey idhar-udhar na kiya jaey. jo aadmi sawab hasil karney key liye Zakat deyga, usey us ka sawab milega aur jo na deyga, hum us sey Zakat to (har soorat) wasul kerengey aur uskey nisf (aadhey) oont bhi zabt kar lengey. Zakat hamarey Rab key faraaiz mein sey eik fariza hai aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key khandan key liye zarra bhar Zakat bhi jayez nahin."
2452,Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein (mujhey) Yamen ki taraf (haakim bana kar) bheja aur hukm diya ke har ghair muslim baligh sey eik deenar (bator jiziya) lun ya uskey barabar muaafiri kapda. aur har tees gaayon mein sey (tabeea) (dusrey saal mein dakhil bachhda ya bichhdi) aur har chaalis gaayon mein sey do daant wala bachhda ya bichhdi (bator zakaat) wasul karun.
2453,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen ki taraf (haakim bana kar) bheja aur mujhey hukm diya ke main har chaalis gaayon mein sey eik do saala (do daantaa) aur har tees mein sey eik saala bachhda ya bichhdi Zakat wasul karun, isi ke sath har baligh (yahudi waghera) sey eik deenar ya uskey barabar yamni kapda (bator jiziya) wasul karun."
2454,Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein (mujhey) Yamen ki taraf bheja to hukm diya ke har tees gaayon mein sey eik saala bachhda ya bichhdi aur har chaalis gaayon mein sey eik do saala (do daantaa) wasul karun aur har (ghair muslim) baligh sey eik deenar ya uskey barabar muaafiri kapda (bator jiziya) wasul karun.
2455,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jab mujhey Yamen bheja to mujhey hukm diya ke main gaayon sey Zakat na lun yahan tak ke wo tees ho jaeyn jab tees ho jaeyn to chaalis tak un mein sey (jazaa) (dusrey saal mein dakhil) nojawan bachhda ya bichhdi Zakat hogi. aur jab wo chaalis ho jaaeyn to un mein do saala (do daantaa) gaaey (muzakkir ya muannas) (bail ya gaaey) Zakat hogi.
2456,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi oonton, gaayon ya bakriyon ka Malik unka haq (un ki zakaat) nahin deyga, usey qiyamat key din eik humwaar khuley maidan mein khada kiya jaeyga. khuron waley janwer usey apney khuron sey kuchleygey gey aur seengon waley janwer usey apney seengon sey takkaren maarengey. un mein sey koi bhi baghair seengon key na hoga aur na kisi key seeng tootey huye hongey. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (zakaat key ilawa) in mein aur kya haq hain? aap ney farmaya : nar jufti key liye dena, pani nikalney key liye dol dena aur Allah key raastey mein (jihad key liye aur faqir waghera zarurat mand ko) bojh laadney aur sawari key liye dena. isi tarah rupey paisey wala agar un ki Zakat nahin deyga to qiyamat key din wo uskey liye eik ganjaa sanp bana diya jaeyga, Malik us sey bhageyga lekin wo sanp uskey peechhey daudeyga aur kahega : main tera wo khazana hun jis key sath to bukhl karta tha. jab Malik ko yaqin ho jaeyga ke us sey bachney ka koi chaara nahin to wo apna haath uskey munh mein dal deyga. wo us ko is tarah chabaaega jis tarah oont chabaataa hai."
2457,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein likha ke ye wo muqarrara sadqaat hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon par laagu farmaai hain aur jin ka Allah Taala ney apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya hai. jis musalman sey Zakat sahih hisab sey talab ki jaey to wo zarur dey aur jis sey zayed maangi jaey to wo na dey. pachchees sey kam oonton mein Zakat har paanch oonton main eik bakri hogi. jab oont pachchees ho jaeyn to paintees tak un mein binte-makhaaz Zakat aayegi. agar binte-makhaaz muyassar na ho to muzakkir ibne-labun diya jaey. jab oont chhattis ho jaeyn to paintaalees tak binte-labun Zakat aayegi. jab chhiyaalees ho jaeyn to saath (60) tak eik hiqqa Zakat hogi jo nar key qabil ho. jab iksath (61) ho jaeyn to pichhattar tak jazaa Zakat hogi. jab chhiyattar (76) ho jaeyn to nawwey tak do bintre-labun Zakat aayegi. aur jab ikkyanwe ho jaeyn to eik sau bees tak do hiqqa Zakat hogi jo nar key qabil hon. jab oont eik sau bees sey badh jaeyn to har chaalis mein binte-labun aur har pachas mein hiqqa Zakat hogi. aur jab oonton ki umrein mukhtalif hon (muqarrara umr key oont na mil saken) to jis shakhs key zimmey jazaa Zakat banti hai lekin uskey paas jazaa na ho balke hiqqa ho to us sey hiqqa hi li jaeygi. aur wo uskey sath do bakriyan bhi deyga, agar usey muyassar hon, warna bees dirham deyga. aur jis shakhs key zimmey hiqqa Zakat banti hai magar uskey paas jazaa hi hai to us sey jazaa hi li jaeygi aur sadqa wasul karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan wapis kerega. aur jis shakhs key zimmey hiqqa Zakat banti ho magar uskey paas hiqqa na ho balke binte-labun ho to wohi li jaeygi aur uskey sath wo do bakriyan deyga, agar usey muyassar hon, warna bees dirham deyga. aur jis shakhs key zimmey binte-laboon banti ho magar uskey paas hiqqa hi ho to us sey wohi li jaeygi aur sadqa wasul karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan deyga. aur jis shakhs key zimmey binte-labun Zakat banti ho, lekin uskey paas binte-labun na ho balke binte-makhaaz ho to us sey wohi ley li jaeygi aur uskey sath wo do bakriyan deyga, agar usey muyassar hon, warna bees dirham deyga. aur jis shakhs key zimmey binte-makhaaz Zakat banti ho lekin uskey paas muzakkir ibne-labun hi ho to wohi us sey liya jaeyga, albatta uskey sath usey kuchh na milega. aur jis aadmi key paas sirf chaar oont hon to un mein koi Zakat nahin magar ye ke Malik khud dena chahey. aur bakriyon ki Zakat jab wo jangal mein charney wali hon aur chaalis hon to eik sau bees tak un main eik bakri hogi. agar eik bhi zayed ho jaey to do sau tak do bakriyan hongi. jab eik bhi badh jaey to teen sau tak teen bakriyan hongi. jab eik bhi ziyada ho jaey to har sau main eik bakri hogi. Zakat mein boodha ya kaanaa (aeb wala) janwer na liya jaeyga. aur muzakkir (nar) bakra bhi nahin liya jaeyga magar ye ke sadqa wasul karney wala lena chahey. alehda alehda rehney waley janweron ko Zakat key dar sey ikhatta nahin kiya jaeyga aur ikhattey rehney waley janweron ko alag alag nahin kiya jaeyga. aur jo Zakat do shareek malikon sey wasul ki jaeygi, wo apney apney janweron key lihaz sey taqseem kar lengey. aur jab charney wali bakriyan chaalis sey eik bhi kam hon to un mein koi Zakat nahin magar ye ke Malik khud dena chahey. aur chaandi mein chaaliswan hissa Zakat hai. agar raqam sirf eik sau nawwey dirham ho to is mein koi Zakat nahin magar ye ke Malik khud dena chahey."
2458,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi oonton, gaayon ya bakriyon ka Malik un ki Zakat ada nahin kerega to qiyamat key din wo janwer us jasaamat aur motaapey sey badh kar ayengey jo (duniya mein) thi. apney seengon sey usey takkaren maarengey aur apney khuron sey usey rondengey. jab un mein sey aakhiri guzar jaeyga to pehley ko dobara laya jaeyga. aur uskey sath yehi sulook hota raheyga yahan tak ke logon key darmiyan faisla kar diya jaey."
2459,Hazrat Suwed bin Ghafala (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamarey paas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey Zakat wasul karney wala shakhs aaya. main uskey paas aaya aur betha. mainey usey ye kehtey huye suna ke mujh sey ye ehad liya gaya hai ke hum doodh peeta bacha ya doodh wala janwer Zakat mein nahin leingey aur alehda alehda janweron ko ikhatta nahin kerengey aur ikhattey janweron ko alehda alehda nahin kerengey. eik shakhs unkey paas oonchi kohaan wali (behtareen) oontni laya aur kehney laga : ye Zakat mein ley lo. us ney inkar kar diya.
2460,Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ko Zakat wasul karney key liye bheja. wo eik shakhs key paas aaya to usney usey eik kamzor sa oont ka bachcha diya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf sey eik shakhs ko sadqa wasul karney key liye bheja lekin falan shakhs ney usey ye kamzor sa oont ka bachcha diya hai. aey Allah ! is mein aur iskey oonton mein barkat na farmana. aap ki ye baat us shakhs ko pahunchi to wo eik khoobsurat oontni ley kar aaya aur arz-pardaz huwa ke main Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney tauba karta hun aur maafi maangta hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! is mein aur iskey oonton mein barkat farma.
2461,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas koi qom apney maalon ki Zakat ley kar aati to aap farmatey : aey Allah ! falan ki aal par rehmat nazil farma. merey walid mohtaram aap key paas apni Zakat ley kar gaey to aap ney farmaya : aey Allah ! Abu Aufaa key khandan par rehmat nazil farma.
2462,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke kuchh erabi (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ki taraf sey Zakat wasul karney waley log hamarey paas aatey hain aur wo zulm kartey hain. aap ney farmaya : sadqa wasul karney walon ko razi karo. unhoney kaha : agar-che wo zulm kerey? aap ney farmaya : sadqa wasul karney walon ko razi karo. wo phir kehney lagey : agar-che wo zulm kerey? aap ney farmaya : sadqa wasul karney walon ko razi karo. Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : jab sey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ye baat suni to merey paas sey koi sadqa wasul karney wala shakhs naraz ho kar nahin gaya, balke khush khush gaya."
2463,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Zakat wasul karney wala (sarkari aadmi) tumharey paas Zakat leney key liye aaye to wo tum sey khush khush wapis jaey."
2464,"Hazrat Muslim bin Safeena bayan kartey hain ke ibne Alqama (Haakim) ney merey walid ko un ki qom ka nambardaar (ya sardar) banaya aur unhein hukm diya ke wo apni qom sey Zakat wasul karen. to merey walid ney mujhey eik qabiley ki taraf bheja taake main un ki Zakat ley kar aaun. main gaya yahan tak ke eik buzurg key paas pahuncha jinhein Hazrat Siaer kaha jata tha. mainey kaha : mujhey walid mohtaram ney tumhari taraf bheja hai taake aap apni bakriyon ki Zakat ada kar den. wo farmaney lagey : aey bhateejey ! tum kis qisam ki bakriyan letey ho? mainey kaha : hum chun kar letey hain yahan tak ke unkey than baalisht key sath maap kar dekhtey hain. wo farmaney lagey : aey bhejtey ! main tujhey batata hun ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein un wadiyon mein sey kisi wadi mein rehta tha. merey paas bakriyan hoti thin. merey paas do aadmi oont par sawar ho kar aaye aur kehney lagey : hum aap ki taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key qaasid hain taake aap apni bakriyon ki Zakat ada karen. mainey kaha : mujh par in bakriyon mein kitni Zakat hai? unhoney kaha : eik bakri. eik aisi bakri jiski qadr aur manzilat main janta tha, mainey wo khalis doodh aur charbi sey bhari hui (behtareen moti tazi doodh wali) bakri pakdi aur unkey paas ley aaya. wo kehney lagey : ye to bachchey wali hai aur hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bachchey wali bakri leney sey mana kiya hai. main eik saal bhar umr ki gabhin bakri, jisney bachcha nahin jana tha jo ke jan'ne key qarib thi, ke (rewad sey) nikal kar unkey paas laya to wo kehney lagey : ye theek hai. hamein pakda do. unhoney usey apney sath oont par laadaa aur chaley gaey."
2465,Hazrat Muslim bin Safinaa sey riwayat hai ke ibne Alqama (Haakim) ney merey walid mohtaram ko apni qom ki Zakat wasul karney key liye muqarrar farmaya. aur phir sabiqa riwayat bayan farmaee.
2466,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zakat ki adaegi ka hukm diya. aap sey kaha gaya ke ibne Jameel, Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed aur Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ney Zakat nahin di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ibne Jameel to is liye naraz hai ke wo faqir tha, Allah Taala ney usey maal-daar bana diya. raha Khalid bin Waleed to tum Khalid par zulm kartey ho. unhoney to apni zirhen aur doosra jangi saaz aur saman Allah Taala key raastey mein waqf kar rakha hai. baqi rahey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key chacha Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib to un ki Zakat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zimmey hai balke uskey sath itni aur hai."
2467,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqey ka hukm diya. sabiqa hadees ki maanind."
2468,Hazrat Abdullah bin Hilal Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : qarib tha ke mujhey aap ki adam mojudgi mein Zakat ki eik bakri ki wajeh sey qatl kar diya jata. aap ney farmaya : agar fuqara aur muhajrin (aur dusrey mustahiqeen) ko Zakat na di jati (un logon ko Zakat deney ki majburi na hoti) to main Zakat wasul hi na karta.
2469,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman par uskey (khidmat waley) ghulam aur (sawari waley) ghodey mein koi Zakat nahin."
2470,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman aadmi par uskey (khidmat waley) ghulam aur (sawari waley) ghodey mein koi Zakat nahin."
2471,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub kartey huye kaha ke aap ney farmaya : musalman par uskey ghulam aur ghodey mein koi Zakat nahin.
2472,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shakhs par uskey ghodey aur ghulam mein koi Zakat nahin."
2473,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman par uskey (khidmat waley) ghulam aur (sawari waley) ghodey mein koi Zakat nahin."
2474,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman par uskey ghulam aur ghodey mein Zakat nahin.
2475,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch Oqiyon sey kam chaandi mein Zakat nahin. na paanch oonton sey kam mein sadqa hai. isi tarah paanch wasq sey kam ghalley mein bhi sadqa (ushr) nahin."
2476,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch wasq sey kam khajuron (ya dusrey ghallon) main koi sadqa (ushr) nahin aur na paanch Oqiyon sey kam chaandi mein Zakat hai aur na paanch oonton sey kam mein Zakat hai."
2477,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : paanch wasq sey kam khajuron mein koi sadqa (ushr) nahin aur na paanch Oqiyon sey kam chaandi mein koi Zakat hai. isi tarah paanch oonton sey kam mein bhi Zakat nahin."
2478,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : paanch Oqiyon (yani (200 dirham) sey kam chaandi mein Zakat nahin aur na paanch oonton sey kam mein Zakat hai. isi tarah paanch wasq (yani 16 man ) sey kam ghalley mein bhi Zakat nahin.
2479,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey ghodon aur ghulamon ki Zakat maaf kar di hai. ab tum apney maal (sona, chaandi aur raqam) ki Zakat do so dirham mein sey paanch dirham ada karo."
2480,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey (sawari key) ghodon aur (khidmat key) ghulamon mein Zakat maaf kar di hai, neez do so dirham sey kam mein Zakat nahin."
2481,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke ilaaqa Yamen ki eik aurat apni beti samet Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui. uski beti key haath mein soney key do bhari kangan they. aap ney farmaya : to inki Zakat ada karti hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya tujhey ye baat pasand hai ke qiyamat key din Allah azz-w-jall tujhey (ya teri beti ko) aag key do kangan pahnaaey? us aurat ney wo kangan fauran utaar diye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf phenk diye aur kehney lagi : ye Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye hain.
2482,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib bayan kartey hain ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai. uskey sath uski eik beti bhi thi jiskey haath mein do kangan they. aagey puri riwayat mazkura baala ki maanind. ye riwayat mursal, yani munqata, hai ( kyonkey Amr bin Shuaib waqiey key aankhon dekhey gawah nahin). Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan farmatey hain : ( sabiqa hadees : 2481 ka raawi) Khalid (is hadees : 2482 key raawi ) Moatamir sey ziyada qabile-bharosa hai."
2483,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal (sona, chaandi aur raqam ) ki Zakat ada nahin karta, qiyamat key din uskey maal ko uskey samney ganjey sanp ki surat mein laya jaeyga jiski aakhon par do siyah nuqtey hongey. wo usey chimat jaeyga ya uskey galey ka toq ban jaeyga aur kahega : main tera khazana hun. main tera khazana hun."
2484,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko Allah Taala maal ata farmaey, phir wo uski zakat na dey to qiyamat key din uskey maal ko uskey samney ganjey sanp ki surat di jaeygi jiski aakhon par do siyah nuqtey hongey. wo us shakhs key munh key dono kinaron ko pakad lega aur kahega : main tera maal hun. main tera khazana hun, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : « { وَ لَا یَحْسَبَنَّ الَّذِیْنَ یَبْخَلُوْنَ بِمَآ اٰتٰہُمُ اللّٰہُ مِنْ فَضْلِہٖ }  jo log us maal mein bukhl kartey hain jo in ko Allah Taala ney apney Fazal o karam sey ata farmaya hai (woh us (bukhl) ko apney liye hergiz behtar na samjhen balke wo unkey liye bura hai aur qiyamat key din wo maal unkey galey ka toq bana diya jaeyga )."
2485,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch wasq sey kam kisi bhi ghalley mein ya khajoor mein Zakat nahin."
2486,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gehun aur khajoor mein Zakat ( ushr ) wajib nahin hoti yahan tak ke wo paanch wasq ho jaeyn. aur chaandi mein Zakat wajib nahin hoti yahan tak ke wo paanch oqiye (do so dirham) ho jaeyn. aur oonton mein Zakat wajib nahin hoti yahan tak ke wo paanch ho jaeyn."
2487,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi daney ( ghalley ) aur khajoor mein Zakat nahin yahan tak ke wo paanch wasq ho jaeyn. aur paanch oonton sey kam mein aur paanch Oqiyon sey kam chaandi mein bhi Zakat nahin."
2488,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch Oqiyon sey kam (chaandi) main Zakat nahin."
2489,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch Oqiyon (200 dirham ) sey kam chaandi mein Zakat nahin, na paanch oonton sey kam mein Zakat hai aur na paanch wasq sey kam ghalley mein Zakat hai."
2490,"Hazrat Salim apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis fasal ko barish, nehrein ya chashmey sairab karen ya wo nami wali ho, is mein daswaan hissa Zakat wajib hai. aur jis fasal ko oonton aur dol (rehet waghera) key zariey sey sairab kya jaey, is mein beeswan hissa Zakat wajib hai."
2491,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis fasal ko barish, nehren aur chashmey sairab keren, is mein daswan hissa zakat hai. aur jis fasal ko oonton key zariey sey sairab kya jaey, is mein beeswan hissa hai."
2492,Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Yamen ki taraf (hakim bana kar) bheja to mujhey hukm diya ke main barish sey sairab honey wali fasal mein sey daswan hissa aur dol w rehet key zariey sey sairab honey wali fasal sey beeswan hissa Zakat wasul karun.
2493,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Masood bin Niyar sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Sahal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas bazar mein tashrif laye aur kehney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jab tum (ushr wasul kartey waqt fasal ya phal ka) andaza lagao to andazey mein sey teesra hissa chhod do. agar teesra hissa na chhodo to chotha hissa zarur chhod do.
2494,Hazrat abu-Umama bin Sahal bin Hanif Allah Taala key farman : « { وَلَا تَیَمَّمُوا الْخَبِیْثَ مِنْہُ تُنْفِقُوْنَ }  tum ( Allah key raastey mein) kharch kartey waqt raddi chiz na diya karo. key barey mein farmatey hain key iska misdaaq « جعرور » aur « لون حبیق » khajuren hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zakat mein raddi aur naqis maal wasul karney sey mana farmaya hai.
2495,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, aap key haath mein asa tha. koi shakhs (masjid mein bator sadqa) raddi qism ki khajoor ka eik khosha latka gaya tha. aap us khoshay par apni lathi maarney lagey aur farmaya : agar us sadqey wala chahta to us sey achi khajoor ka sadqa kar sakta tha. bilashuba is qism ka sadqa karney wala qiyamat key din raddi khajuren hi khayega."
2496,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey giri padi chiz key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : jo chiz aamad o raft waley raastey sey ya abad basti sey miley to us ka eik saal tak aelan karo. agar uska Malik aa jaey to theek hai warna wo tumharey liye jayez hai. aur jo chiz aamad o raft waley raastey sey ya abad basti sey na miley to aisi chiz aur madfun khazana (milney ki soorat) main panchwan hissa hai.
2497,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : janwer ka kya huwa nuqsan rayegan hai, kunwen ka nuqsan rayegan hai aur madani kaan ka nuqsan bhi rayegan hai. aur madfun khazaney mein paanchwan hissa hai."
2498,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey aisi hi riwayat naqal ki hai.
2499,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : janwer ka lagaya huwa zakham rayegaan hai aur kunwen ki wajeh sey honey wala nuqsan rayegan hai. aur madani kaan ki wajeh sey honey wala nuqsan bhi rayegaan hai aur madfun khazana (milney ki soorat) main paanchwan hissa (baitul-mal ka) hai."
2500,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kunwen ki wajeh sey honey wala nuqsan rayegan hai, janwer ka lagaya huwa zakham rayegan hai aur kaan (maadani) ki wajeh sey honey wala nuqsan bhi rayegaan hai, aur madfun shuda khazana (mil jaey to us) main sey paanchwan hissa (baitul-maal ka) hoga."
2501,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Hilal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas apney shehad ki Zakat ley kar aaye aur aap sey arz kya ke aap ( shehad wali ) wadi Salba unkey liye makhsus farma den. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wo wadi unkey liye makhsus farma di, phir jab Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa baney to ( wahan key Hakim ) Sufiyan bin Wahab ney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey us barey mein daryaaft karney key liye khat likha to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney jawaban likha ke agar wo tujhey apney shehad ka ushr ada kartey rahen jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ada kya kartey they to wadi Salba unkey liye makhsus rakho warna ye barishi makkhi (ka shehad) hai, jo chahey usey khaye ."
2502,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzanul-Mubarak ka sadqa (sadqatul-fitr) har azad, ghulam, muzakkir aur muannas (mard aur aurat) par khajoor aur jau ka eik saa muqarrar farmaya tha. baad mein logon ney uski jagah gehun ka nisf (aadha) saa thehra liya."
2503,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqatul-fitr har muzakkir, muannas , azad aur ghulam par khajoor ya jau ka eik saa muqarrar farmaya hai. baad mein logon ney gehun key nisf (aadha) saa ko ikhtiyar kar liya."
2504,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzan ki Zakat (sadqatul-fitr) har chhotey, badey, azad, ghulam aur muzakkir aur muannas (mard aur aurat) par khajoor aur jau ka eik saa muqarrar farmaya hai."
2505,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Ramzanul-Mubarak ka sadqa fitr har azad, ghulam, muzakkir aur muannas (mard aur aurat) musalman par khajoor aur jau sey eik saa muqarrar farmaya hai."
2506,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqatul-fitr har chhotey, badey, muzakkar, muannas, azad aur ghulam musalman par khajoor aur jau sey eik saa muqarrar farmaya hai aur hukm diya hai ke is ki adaegi namaze-eid key liye janey sey pehley ki jaey."
2507,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqatul-fitr har chhotey, badey, muzakkar, muannas (mard aur aurat), azad aur ghulam par khajoor aur jau sey eik saa farz (muqarrar) kiya hai."
2508,Hazrat Qais bin Saad bin Ubada sey marwi hai ke hum Aashura (10 Muharramul-Haram) ka roza rakhtey they aur sadqatul-fitr ada kiya kartey they. jab Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozon aur Zakat ki farziyat nazil hui to na hamein is ka naya hukm diya gaya aur na us sey roka gaya. wesey hum ye kaam kartey rahey.
2509,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqatul-fitr (ki adaegi) ka hukm Zakat (ki farziyat) utarney sey pehley diya tha. jab Zakat (ki farziyat) nazil hui to na aap ney is ka (naya) hukm diya aur na is sey mana farmaya. hum is (sadqatul-fitr) ko ada kartey rahey. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Abu Ammaar ka naam Uraib bin Humed hai, Amr bin Shurehbil ki kunniyat Abu Maisraa hai. Salma bin Kuheil ney is hadees ki sanad key bayan mein Hukm ki mukhalifat ki hai, lekin Hukm Salma bin Kuheil sey ziyada qabile-bharosa hain."
2510,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney, jab wo Basra key haakim they, maahe-Ramzanul-Mubarak key aakhir mein (khutba diya) farmaya : apney rozon ki Zakat (sadqatul-fitr) nikalo. log eik dusrey ki taraf dekhney lagey. aap ney farmaya : yahan jo Madina Munawra key log hain uthen aur apney (Basri) bhaiyon ko taalim den kyonkey wo nahin jantey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye sadqa har muzakkir aur muannas (mard aur aurat) aur azad aur ghulam par khajoor aur jau ka eik saa aur gehun ka aadha saa farz kiya hai. to log uthey. Hisham ney Humed ki mukhalifat ki hai, us ney (Hasan key bajaey) ibne Sirin ka naam liya hai."
2511,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney sadqatul-fitr ka zikr kartey huye farmaya : sadqatul-fitr gehun, khajoor, jau ya sulat sey eik saa ada karo."
2512,Hazrat Abu-Rijaa sey riwayat hai unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko tumharey yani Basrey key member par khutba irshad farmatey suna ke sadqatul-fitr har khaai janey wali chiz sey eik saa hai. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye (is hadees ka raawi Ayub) teeno mein sey ziyada qawi hai.
2513,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqatul-fitr jau, khushk khajoor ya paneer sey eik saa muqarrar farmaya hai."
2514,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hum mein mojud they to hum sadqatul-fitr tuaam (gehun ya har khurak wala ghalla) jau, khushk khajoor, kishmish ya paneer sey eik saa diya kartey they."
2515,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hum mein tashrif farma they to hum sadqatul-fitr tuaam (khaaney ki cheez) khajoor, jau ya paneer sey eik saa nikala kartey they. hum isi tarah nikaltey rahey yahan tak ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Sham sey (Madina Munawwara) aaye to jo baaten unhoney logon ko sikhaain, un mein sey eik ye bhi thi ke unhoney farmaya : main samajhta hun Shami gehun key do mudd qeemat mein khajoor waghera key saa key barabar hain. to logon ney is par amal shuru kar diya."
2516,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein hum khajoor, jau, kishmish, aataa, paneer ya salat waghera sey eik saa hi (sadqatul-fitr) detey they, phir raawi Sufiyan ko shak huwa aur unhoney kaha : aataa ya salat."
2517,"Hazrat Hasan Basri sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Basrey mein khutba irshad farmaya, jis mein kaha : apney rozon ki Zakat ada karo. log (tajjub sey) eik dusrey ko dekhney lagey to aap ney farmaya : yahan jo log Madina Munawra sey aaye huye hain, wo apney (Basri) bhaiyon ki taraf uth kar jaeyn aur unhein taalim den kyonkey wo nahin jantey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqatul-fitr har chhotey, badey, azad, ghulam aur muzakkir aur muannas (mard aur aurat) par gehun ka nisf (aadha) saa aur khajoor ya jau ka eik saa muqarrar farmaya hai. Hazrat Hasan Basri ney kaha ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab Allah Taala ney tumhen maal ki wusat ata farmaee hai to tum bhi wusat ikhtiyar karo, yani gehun ho ya koi aur ghalla, sab mein sey pura saa hi do."
2518,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-muqaddas mein log sadqatul-fitr jau, khajoor, salat ya kishmish sey eik saa diya kartey they."
2519,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein hum (sadqatul-fitr) jau, khajoor, kishmish ya paneer sey eik saa nikala kartey they. aur (baad mein bhi) hum isi tarah nikaltey rahey yahan tak ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aa gaya to unhoney farmaya : main samajhta hun ke Sham ki gehun key do mudd (aadha saa) jo key eik saa key barabar hain."
2520,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein (sadqatul-fitr ) khajoor ya jo ya paneer sey eik saa hi diya kartey they. hum unkey ilawa aur koi chiz na diya kartey they.
2521,Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein saa tumharey aaj kal key hisab sey eik mudd aur eik tihai mudd key barabar tha. ab us ( mudd ki miqdaar ) main izafa kar diya gaya hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey ye hadees Ziyad bin Ayub ney bhi bayan ki hai.
2522,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke sadqatul-fitr eid ki namaz key liye janey sey pehley ada kar diya jaey. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key ustaad) Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Bazee ney (apni riwayat mein «bi-sadqatul-fitr» key bajaey ) «bi-zakatul-fitr» key alfaz bayan kiye hain.
2523,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen ki taraf ( haakim bana kar) bheja aur farmaya : to wahan ehle-kitab ( yahudiyon ) ki Kasir jamaat ki taraf ja raha hai, lihaza unhein dawat dena ke wo gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala ka Rasool hun. agar wo teri ye baat maan lein to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ney un par paanch namazein har din raat mein farz ki hain. agar wo teri ye baat bhi maan lein to batana ke Allah azz-w-jall ney un par unkey maalon mein Zakat farz ki hai jo unkey maal daar logon sey li jaeygi aur unkey faqir logon mein taqseem ki jaeygi. aur agar wo teri ye baat bhi maan lein to unkey umda maal na lena. aur mazloom ki baddua sey bachna kyonkey Allah Taala tak pahunchney mein uskey samney koi rukawat nahin."
2524,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( Bani-Israel mein sey) eik aadmi ney kaha : main aaj zarur sadqa karunga. wo (raat key waqt ) apna sadqa ley kar nikla aur ja kar eik chor key haath par rakh diya, to subh log ye kehney lagey ke chor par sadqa kya gaya hai. us ney kaha : aey Allah ! tera shukr hai (agar-che) chor par sadqa ho gaya. aaj main phir sadqa karunga. wo sadqa ley kar nikla to kisi zaaniya key haath par rakh aaya. subh log ye kehney lagey ke raat eik bad-kar aurat par sadqa kya gaya. us aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah tera shukr hai ( agar-che ) zaaniya par sadqa ho gaya hai. aaj phir main sadqa karunga, phir wo apna sadqa ley kar nikla. eik ghani ko dey aaya. subh log chemegoiyan karney lagey ke (tajjub hai) maaldaar par sadqa kya gaya hai. wo shakhs kehney laga, aey Allah tera! shukr hai ( ajeeb baat hai) kabhi bad-kar aurat par sadqa ho jata hai, kabhi chor par aur kabhi maal daar par, phir khuwab mein us sey kaha gaya : tera sadqa to yaqinan qubul ho chuka. rahi zaaniya! ( yani is par kya huwa sadqa ) to ( wo isliye qubul hai ke ) shayad us sadqey ki wajeh sey wo bad-kari sey baaz aa jaey. aur chor! shayad wo is (sadqey) ki wajeh sey chori karney sey baaz aa jaey aur maaldaar! shayad wo ibrat o nasihat hasil karey aur Allah Taala key diye huye maal sey kharch karney lagey."
2525,"Hazrat abu-Mulaih key walid sey marwi hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : Allah Taala tahaarat key baghair namaz qubul nahin karta aur haram maal sey sadqa qubul nahin karta."
2526,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab bhi koi shakhs halal maal sey sadqa karta hai, aur Allah Taala qubul bhi halal maal hi farmata hai, to Allah Taala usey apney daeyn haath mein wasul karta hai, agar-che wo sadqa eik khajoor hi ho, phir wo khajoor rabe-rahmaan ki hatheli mein badhti rehti hai yahan tak ke wo pahad sey bhi badi ho jati hai, jaisey tum mein sey koi shakhs apney ghodey ya oont key bachey ko paalta-posta hai."
2527,Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi Khashami (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : aisa eman jis mein koi shak na rahey. aur aisa jihad jis mein koi khayanat na ki jaey aur neki wala saaf suthra hajj. puchha gaya : kon si namaz afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : lambey qiyam wali (nafl namaz). puchha gaya : sadqa kon sa afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : kam maal waley ka mashaqqat sey kamaya huwa maal. puchha gaya : hijrat kon si afzal hai? farmaya is shakhs ki jo Allah Taala ki haram karda chizon ko chhod dey. arz kya gaya : jihad kon sa afzal hai? aap ney farmaya is shakhs ka jisney apney jaan o maal key sath mushrekin sey jihad kya. arz kya gaya : kon sa qatl (maara jana) ziyada sharf wala hai? aap ney farmaya is aadmi ki shahadat jiska apna khoon bhi baha diya gaya aur uska ghoda bhi maar diya gaya ho.
2528,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( kabhi ) eik dirham (ka sawab ) lakh dirham sey badh jata hai. sahaba ney puchha : wo kaisey? aap ney farmaya : eik aadmi key paas kul do dirham hon, usney un mein sey eik sadqa kar diya. aur doosra shakhs apney maal key eik koney mein gaya. is mein sey eik lakh dirham uthaya aur sadqa kar diya."
2529,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( kabhi ) eik dirham lakh dirham sey badh jata hai. sahaba ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kaisey ? aap ney farmaya : eik aadmi key paas kal do dirham hun, aur wo un mein sey eik uthaey aur sadqa kar dey. aur dusrey shakhs key paas bahut sa maal ho, us ney apney maal key eik kinarey sey eik lakh dirham uthaya aur sadqa kar diya."
2530,"Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamen sadqa karney ka hukm farmaya kartey they. hum mein sey kuch log koi chiz na paatey they ke sadqa karen to wo bazar jatey aur apni peeth par bojh uthatey (baar bardari ka kaam kartey ) aur eik mudd ley kar aatey aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dey detey, lekin aaj mein aisey log dekhta hun jinkey paas lakhon dirham hain magar un dino unkey paas eik dirham bhi nahin hota tha."
2531,Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqa karney ka hukm diya to Hazrat abu-Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ney nisf saa sadqa kya. eik aur sahabi us sey bahut ziyada maal ley kar aaye. munafiq kehney lagey : Allah Taala us shakhs (Hazrat abu-Aqeel ) key us qaleel sadqey sey be-niaz hai aur us dusrey shakhs ney sirf riyakari key liye sadqa kya hai. to ye aayat utri : « { اَلَّذِیْنَ یَلْمِزُوْنَ الْمُطَّوِّعِیْنَ … الآیۃ }  munafiq log khushi sey Kasir sadqa karney waley eman walon ko bhi aeb lagatey hain aur un gharib musalmanon ko bhi jinkey paas mashaqqat sey kamaya huwa thoda sa maal hai.
2532,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ( maal ) manga, aap ney mujhey diya. mainey phir manga, aap ney phir diya. mainey phir manga, aap ney phir diya. sath hi farmaya : bilashuba ye maal sabz (hara) o sheereen hai. jo shakhs usey dil ki pakizgi key sath lega, uskey liye is mein barkat hogi aur jo dil key tama o hirs key sath lega, uskey liye is mein barkat na hogi aur wo us shakhs ki tarah hoga jo khata hai magar sair nahin hota aur ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey behtar hai."
2533,"Hazrat Tariq Mahaaribi (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum Madina Munawra aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey logon sey khitab farma rahey they. aap farma rahey they : deney waley ka haath ooncha hota hai aur sab sey pehley to usey dey jiska to zimmedar hai. apni maa ko dey, apney baap ko dey, apni behen ko dey, apney bhai ko dey, phir apney qaribi rishtedar ko dey, phir apney padosi ko dey. ye hadees mukhtasar hai."
2534,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sadqa karney aur maangney sey bachney ka zikr kartey huye farmaya : ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey behtar hai. ooper wala haath deney wala haath hai aur nichey wala haath maangney wala hai.
2535,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen sadqa wo hai jis key baad bhi sadqa karney wala ghani rahey. aur ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey behtar hai. aur sab sey usey pehley dey jis ka to zimmedaar hai."
2536,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sadqa karo. eik aadmi ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! merey paas eik deenar hai. aap ney farmaya : apney aap par kharch kar. us ney kaha : merey paas eik aur hai. aap ney farmaya : apni biwi par kharch kar. us ney arz kya : merey paas eik aur hai. farmaya : apni aulad par kharch kar. wo kehney laga: merey paas eik aur hai. aap ney farmaya : apney naukar par kharch kar. wo bola : merey paas eik aur hai. aap ney farmaya : phir to ziyada janta hai (ke kahan kharch karey )."
2537,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Jumey key din masjid mein dakhil huwa jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they. aap ney farmaya : do rakatein padh. phir wo dusrey Jumey ko aaya to (us waqt bhi ) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they. aap ney farmaya : do rakatein padh. phir wo teesrey Jumey ko aaya to (us waqt bhi aap khutba farma rahey they) aap ney phir farmaya : do rakatein padh. phir farmaya : sadqa karo. logon ney sadqa kya. aap ney usey do kapdey diye. phir aap ney farmaya : sadqa karo. usney apney do kapdon mein sey eik kapda phenk diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum usey nahin dekhtey? ye kharab haalat mein masjid mein dakhil huwa. mujhey ummid thi ke tum khud hi samajh jaogey aur is par sadqa karogey lekin tum ney na diya to mainey khud kaha ke sadqa karo. tum ney sadqa kya to mainey usey do kapdey diye, phir mainey kaha : sadqa karo to usney bhi apna eik kapda phenk diya. utha apna kapda. aur aap ney usey daanta."
2538,Hazrat Umer Mola Aabi Lehem (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mujhey merey Malik ney hukm diya ke main kuch gosht tayyar karun. ittifaaq se eik miskeen aa gaya. mainey kuch usey khila diya. merey Malik ko uska ilm huwa to usney mujhey maara. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya (aur shikayat ki ). aap ney usey bulaya aur farmaya : tu ney usey kyon maara? us ney kaha : ye meri ijazat key baghair mera khana (fuqara ko) khilata hai. aap ney farmaya : (phir kya huwa?) sawab tum dono ko milega.
2539,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har musalman key zimmey sadqa ( wajib ) hai. puchha gaya ke aap bataeyn, agar uskey paas kuch na ho to? aap ney farmaya : apney haath sey kamai kerey. apney aap ko faeyda pahunchaey aur sadqa bhi kerey. kaha gaya : aap bataeyn agar wo aisey na kar sakey to? aap ney farmaya : kisi hajat mand, sitam-raseeda (mazloom ya aajiz) ki madad kar dey. arz kya gaya ke agar wo aisey bhi na kar sakey to? aap ney farmaya : phir neki ka hukm dey. arz kya gaya : agar wo ye bhi na kar sakey to? aap ney farmaya : burai sey baaz rahey. ye bhi eik sadqa hai."
2540,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi aurat apney khawind key ghar sey sadqa karti hai to usey bhi sawab milta hai, khawind ko bhi aur khazanchi ko bhi. lekin un mein sey koi kisi key sawab sey kami nahin karta. khawind ko isliye ke us ney ye maal kamaya tha aur aurat ko isliye ke us ney kharch kya."
2541,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makka Mukarrama fateh kya to khutbey key liye khadey huye aur aap ney apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya : kisi aurat key liye jayez nahin ke khawind ki ijazat key baghair koi tohfa ya Atiya dey. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
2542,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaje-mutahrat aap key paas ikhatti huin aur kehney lagen : hum mein sey kon aap sey jaldi milegi? aap ney farmaya : jis key haath sab sey lambey hongey. unhoney eik baans sey haath mapney shuru kar diye ( wo aapki murad yehi samjhin jiska haath lamba ho). (is lihaz sey) Hazrat sauda (Raziallahu anha) aap sey jaldi milney wali thin kyonkey unkey haath un sab sey lambey they. (darasal) us sey murad sadqey ki kasrat thi.
2543,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik aadmi ney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool! kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : to is haal mein sadqa karey ke to tandurust ho aur maal ka khahish mand ho. zindagi ki ummid rakhta ho aur faqr sey darta ho."
2544,Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : afzal sadqa wo hai jis key baad ghina baqi rahey aur ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey behtar hai. aur sab sey pehley us shakhs ko dey jis ka to zimmey daar hai.
2545,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen sadqa wo hai jis key baad ghina baqi rahey aur pehley us shakhs ko dey jis ka to zimmedar (kafeel) hai."
2546,Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi apney ghar walon par sawab ki niyat sey kharch karey to wo uskey liye sadqa hai.
2547,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Banu Azra ( qabiley ) key eik aadmi ney apney ghulam ko apni maut key baad azad kar diya. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ney farmaya : terey paas uskey ilawa koi aur maal hai? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : usey mujh sey kon khareedega ? to Hazrat Naeem bin Abdullah Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey aath so dirham mein kharid liya aur wo ye raqam ley kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. aap ney ye raqam us shakhs key supurd ki, phir farmaya : sab sey pehley apney aap par kharch kar. agar kuch bach jaey to wo terey ghar walon key liye hai. agar ghar walon ( ki zarooriyat) sey kuch bach jaey to wo terey qurbat daaron key liye hai. aur agar terey qurbat daaron sey bhi bach jaey to phir to usey apney aagey aur apney daeyn baeyn sadqa kar."
2548,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sadqa karney waley ki aur kanjus shakhs ki misal un do aadmiyon ki tarah hai jinkey jism par lohey key kurtey ya zirhen hon, jinhoney unkey seenon ko dhanp rakha ho. jab sakhi kharch karney ka irada karta hai to uski zireh khul jati hai aur wasee ho jati hai yahan tak ke uski ungliyon key poron ko dhanp leti hai aur uskey nishaanate-qadam ko mita deti hai. aur jab bakheel kharch karney ka irada karta hai to uski zireh sikud jati hai aur har kadi apni jagah simat jati hai yahan tak ke uskey halaq ya galey ko pakad leti hai. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha (jaisey) aap usey khol rahey hain aur wo khulti nahin. (Hazrat Abu-Hurera key shagrid) Taus ney kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bhi apney haath sey usey kholney ka ishara kartey they lekin wo khulti na thi."
2549,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kanjus ki aur sadqa karney waley ki misal un do aadmiyon ki tarah hai jin par lohey ki zirhen hain aur unkey haath unkey seeney key ooper bandhey huye hain. sadqa karney wala shakhs jab sadqa karney ka irada karta hai to uski zireh khul jati hai. yahan tak ke uskey nishanaate-qadam tak ko mita daalti hai. aur jab bakheel aadmi sadqey ka irada karta hai to zireh ki har kadi dusri kadi sey jud jati (us mein pewast ho jati) hai aur zireh sikud jati hai aur uskey haath seeney sey bandhey rehtey hain. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : wo zireh ko kholney ki puri koshish karta hai lekin wo khulti nahin."
2550,"Hazrat abu-Umama bin Sahal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum eik din muhajrin o ansaar ki eik jamaat key sath masjide-nabwi mein bethey they ke hamney Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas eik shakhs ko bheja taake wo hamarey liye (unkey yahan hazir honey ki) ijazat talab kerey. ( ijazat milney par) hum un ki khidmat mein hazir huye to unhoney farmaya ke eik dafa eik saail merey paas aaya. merey paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif farma they. mainey (laundi sey) usey kuch deney ko kaha, phir mainey wo chiz mangwaya kar dekhi (ke wo kis qadr hai?) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aaisha! to chahti hai ke terey ghar mein koi chiz terey ilm key baghair na aaye aur na (wahan sey) jaey? mainey arz kya : ji haan! aap ney farmaya : Aaisha! aisey na karo. gin-gin kar sadqa na kya karo, warna Allah Taala bhi tujhey gin-gin kar dega."
2551,"Hazrat Asma bint abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya tha : gin-gin kar Allah key raastey mein na dey warna Allah Taala bhi tujhey gin-gin kar dega."
2552,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir hui aur arz kya : aey Allah key Nabi ! merey paas zaati maal to koi nahin magar jo (merey khawind) Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey la kar detey hain, kya mujhey gunah hoga agar main ussey Atiya waghera dun? aap ney farmaya : jitni gunjaaish ho, atiye dey aur baandh baandh kar na rakh warna Allah Taala bhi tujh par baandh dega."
2553,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag sey bacho agar-che khajoor key eik tukdey hi key zariey sey.
2554,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aag ka zikr farmaya, phir aap ney ( nafrat o karahat sey) apna munh pheraa aur aag sey Allah ki panah talab ki. Shoba ( raawi ) ney kaha ke aap ney teen dafa aisey hi kya, phir aap ney farmaya : ( jahannam ki ) aag sey bacho agar-che khajoor key eik tukdey hi key zariey sey. agar ye bhi na miley to achi baat hi kar key ( aag sey bacho )."
2555,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum din key aaghaz mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir they ke kuch log aaye, nangey badan, nangey paon, talwaarein latkaaey huye. wo aksar balke sabkey sab muzir qabiley sey they. unki tang haali aur bhook dekh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra anwar mutghaiyar (ghamzada) ho gaya. aap andar (ghar) gaey (magar kuch na mila to) phir bahar tashrif ley aaye aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Azan deney ka hukm diya. unhoney Azan o iqaamat kahi. aap ney jamaat karwai, phir aap ney khutba irshad farmaya : { یٰٓاَیُّھَا النَّاسُ اتَّقُوْا … رَقِیْبًا } padhi. aey logo ! apney rab sey daro jisney tum sab ko eik jaan sey paida farmaya aur us sey uski biwi paida ki aur phir un dono sey bahut sey mard aur aurten phelaey . aur Allah Taala sey dartey raho jis ka naam lekar eik dusrey sey maangtey ho aur rishtey todney sey ( bhi ) daro. yaqinan Allah Taala tum par nigraan hai. « { وَاتَّقُوْا اللّٰہَ … لِغَدٍ }  Allah Taala sey daro aur har shakhs dekhey ke usney kal (agli zindagi) key liye kya aagey bheja hai. aadmi apney deenar sey sadqa kerey. apney dirham sey sadqa kerey. apney kapdey sey sadqa kerey. gehun ka saa dey, khajoor ka saa dey. yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : chahey khajoor ka tukda hi sadqa kerey. ansaar mein sey eik aadmi itni bhari theli utha kar laya ke uski hatheli us sey aajiz ho rahi thi balke aajiz ho hi gaee thi, phir to logon ka taanta bandh gaya yahan tak ke mainey do dher dekhay. eik ghalley ka aur eik kapdon ka, yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra anwar yun (khushi sey) damakney laga goya ke is par sona chadha diya gaya ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Islam mein koi achcha tariqa jari kya, usey apna sawab bhi milega aur jitney log usey dekh kar wo kaam kerengey, unkey ajr mein sey bhi usey hissa milega, baghair uskey ke unkey sawab mein koi kami ho. isi tarah jo shakhs Islam mein bura kaam jari kar dey, is par us ka apna gunah bhi hoga aur un logon ka bhi jo usey dekh kar wo kaam kerengey, lekin us sey unkey gunahon mein koi kami na hogi."
2556,"Hazrat Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : sadqa karo isliye ke eik aisa zamana aaney wala hai ke aadmi sadqa ley kar chalega. (ke kisi ko dey) magar jisey wo sadqa diya jaeyga, wo kahega : agar to kal ley aata to main qubul kar leta, aaj nahin."
2557,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sifarish karo. tumhari sifarish qubul ki jaeygi. aur Allah Taala apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani jo chahega, faisla farmaeyga."
2558,"Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi mujh sey koi chiz maangta hai aur main inkar kar deta hun taake tum sifarish karkey sawab hasil karo. tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sifarish kya karo, tumhein sawab milega."
2559,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik ghairat wo hai jisey Allah azz-w-jall pasand farmata hai aur eik ghairat wo hai jisey Allah Taala napasand farmata hai. isi tarah eik fakhr wo hai jisey Allah Taala pasand farmata hai aur eik fakhr wo hai jisey Allah Taala napasand farmata hai. pasandida ghairat wo hai jo tohmat key maqam par ho aur naa-pasandida ghairat wo hai jo bula wajeh ho. isi tarah Allah Taala ka pasandida fakhr wo hai jo aadmi ladaai key waqt karey ya sadqa kartey waqt. aur naa-pasandida fakhr wo hai jo batil mein ho."
2560,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khao aur sadqa karo aur libas pahno magar fuzul kharchi aur takabbur na ho."
2561,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik momin dusrey momin key liye imarat ki tarah hai ke uska eik hissa dusrey hissey ko mazbut karta hai. neez farmaya : amanat daar khaazin jo khush dili sey wo chiz (Allah key raastey mein) deta hai, jiska usey hukm diya gaya ho, wo bhi sadqa karney walon mein shumar hota hai."
2562,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : buland aawaz sey Quran Majeed padhney wala, elania sadqa karney waley ki tarah hai aur aahista Quran padhney wala chupa kar sadqa karney waley ki tarah."
2563,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey hain ke Allah Taala qiyamat key din unki taraf nahin dekhega : waliden ka nafarman, mardon ki mushaabihat ikhtiyar karney wali aurat aur be-ghairat khawind, neez teen shakhs jannat mein dakhil na hongey : maa-baap ka nafarman, hamesha sharab peeney wala aur de kar ehsan jatlaaney wala."
2564,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey (bad-naseeb) hain ke Allah Taala qiyamat key din unhein (nazare-rehmat sey) nahin dekhega. na unsey (raza mandi wala) kalam farmaeyga aur na unhein pak farmaeyga aur unkey liye dardnak azab hoga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aayat ka ye tukda qirat farmaya to Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : wo to nakam huye aur khasaray mein padey. wo to nakam huye aur khasaray mein padey. ( wo kon log hain? ) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( wo ye hain : ) apney tehband ko takhney sey nichey latkaaney wala, jhooti qism kha kar apna saman bechney wala aur apney atiye par ehsan jatlaaney wala."
2565,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey (bad-nasib) hain ke qiyamat key din Allah Taala unsey kalam nahin farmaeyga aur na unki taraf dekhega aur na unhein pak farmaeyga aur unkey liye dardnak azab hai : apney atiye ka ehsan jatlaaney wala, apney tehband ko takhney sey nichey latkaaney wala aur jhooti qism kha kar saman bechney wala."
2566,"Hazrat ibne-Bajeed Ansari ki dadi bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawali ko kuch na kuch dey kar wapis karo, chahey jala huwa khur hi ho."
2567,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada ney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab koi shakhs apney Malik key paas jaey aur us sey uski zarurat sey zayed koi chiz maangey aur wo usey na dey to us Malik key liye qiyamat key din eik ganja sanp bulaya jaeyga jo uskey zayed maal ko chabaeyga, jo us ney nahin diya."
2568,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala ka wasta dey kar panah talab kerey. usey panah do. jo shakhs Allah Taala key naam par maangey, usey do. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala key naam par aman maangey, usey aman do. aur jo shakhs tum sey husne-suluk kerey. usey uska badla do aur agar tumhein badla deney ko kuch na miley to uskey liye dua karo (aur kartey raho) yahan tak ke tumhein yaqin ho jaey ke tumney uskey ehsan ka badla chuka diya hai."
2569,Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Heda Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Nabi! mainey aap key paas aaney sey qabl apney haath ki ungliyon ki tadaad sey bhi ziyada qasmen khai thin ke na main aap key paas aaunga aur na aap ka Deen qubul karunga. aur main Deen ki koi samajh nahin rakhta magar jo Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool mujhey sikhaein. aur main aap sey Allah Taala ki zaat key wastey sey sawal karta hun ke Allah Taala ney aap ko kya chiz dey kar hamarey paas bheja hai? aap ney farmaya : Islam dey kar. mainey arz kya : Islam ki alaamaat kya hain? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to kahey : mainey apni zaat ko Allah Taala key tabey kar diya hai aur (us key ilawa har chiz sey) alehda ho jaey aur namaz qaaim karey aur Zakat ada kerey. har musalman dusrey musalman key liye qabile-ehtiraam hai. wo dono eik dusrey key madadgar bhai hotey hain. Allah Taala kisi mushrik sey uskey Islam laney key baad bhi koi amal qubul nahin farmata yahan tak ke wo mushrekin ko chhod kar musalmanon sey aa miley.
2570,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tumhen na bataun ke logon mein sey behtareen rutbey wala kon shakhs hai? hamney arz kya : kyon nahin, aey Allah key Rasool! (zarur bataeyn!) aap ney farmaya : wo aadmi jo Allah Taala key raastey mein apna ghodaa liye phirta hai yahan tak ke usey maut aa jati hai ya wo shaheed ho jata hai. aur main tumhein wo shakhs bataun jo uskey qarib hai? hamney kaha : ji haan! aey Allah key Rasool! aap ney farmaya : wo shakhs jo kisi pahad ki ghaati mein alehda rehta hai, namaz qaaim karta hai, Zakat ada karta hai aur logon key shar sey alehda rehta hai, neez bataun, bad-tareen shakhs kon hai? hamney kaha : ji haan aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : jo Allah key naam par khud to ( logon sey) maangey, lekin uskey naam par (kisi ko) na dey."
2571,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey hain ke Allah Taala un sey mohabbat farmata hai aur teen shakhs aisey hain ke Allah Taala un sey bughz rakhta hai. jin sey Allah Taala mohabbat farmata hai (woh ye hain :) eik aadmi kisi qom key paas aaya. un sey Allah Taala key naam par sawal kya. kisi bahami (aapsi) qurbat ki bina par sawal nahin kya, lekin unhoney usey kuch na diya. eik shakhs (un mein sey utha aur) un logon ko peechey chhod kar aagey nikal gaya aur usey khufiya taor par diya. uskey us atiye ko Allah Taala ney jana ya us shakhs ney jisey us ney diya. (doosra ye ke) kuch log sari raat chaltey rahey, yahan tak ke jab neend unhein har us chiz sey achi lagney lagi jo neend key barabar ho sakti hai to wo sawariyon sey utar padey aur so gaey, lekin eik shakhs (namaz mein) khada ho kar merey samney gidgidaney laga aur meri aayaat tilawat karney laga. teesra wo shakhs jo eik lashkar mein tha. unka dushman sey muqabla huwa. sab bhag khadey huye magar wo data raha, yahan tak ke shaheed ho gaya ya usey fatah mil gaee. aur wo teen shakhs jin sey Allah azz-w-jall bughz rakhta hai, ye hain : boodha zina kaar, faqir mutakabbir aur maal daar zalim."
2572,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : miskeen wo nahin jis ko eik khajur, do khajuren ya eik luqma, do luqmey wapis kar den, balke miskeen wo hai jo hajat mand honey key bawajud maangney sey perhez kerey. tum chaho to ye aayat padh lo : « { لَا یَسْئَلُوْنَ النَّاسَ اِلْحَافًا }  (sadqaat key mustahiq wo log hain) jo maangtey waqt logon key galey nahin pad jatey."
2573,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye ghoomney phirney wala shakhs miskeen nahin jisey eik do luqmey ya eik do khajuren palta deti hain. sahaba ney arz kya : to phir miskeen kon hai? aap ney farmaya : jiskey paas itna maal na ho ke guzaara kar sakey. na us (key faqr) ka kisi ko pata hi chalta hai ke is par sadqa kya jaey aur na wo khud khada ho kar logon sey maangta hai."
2574,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : miskeen wo nahin jisey eik do luqmey ya eik do khajuren palta deti hain. logon ney kaha : to aey Allah key Rasool! phir miskeen kon hai? aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs itna maal nahin rakhta jo kifaayat kar sakey aur logon ko us ( key faqr ) ka pata nahin chalta ke is par sadqa ho sakey."
2575,"Hazrat Umme-Bujed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai. aur unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baiat karney ka sharf hasil hai. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke kabhi koi miskeen saail merey darwazey par aa khada hota hai magar merey paas usey deney key liye kuch nahin hota. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar usey deney key liye terey paas kuch bhi na ho siwaye jaley huye khur key, to wohi usey dey dey."
2576,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey hain ke Allah Taala qiyamat key din un sey kalam nahin farmaeyga. boodha bad-kar, maghroor o mutakabbir faqir aur jhoota badshah."
2577,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : char logo sey Allah Taala bughz rakhta hai : jhooti qasmen kha kar saman bechney wala, maghroor aur mutakabbir faqir, boodha zina kaar aur zalim badshah."
2578,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa aur miskeen key liye dod-dhoop karney wala us shakhs ki tarah hai jo Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karta hai."
2579,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney jab wo Yamen key ameer they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ghair saaf shuda soney ki dali bheji. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey chaar aadmiyon key darmiyan taqseem farma diya : Aqra bin Habis Hanzali, Uena bin Badr Fazaari, Alqama bin Ulaasa Aamiri jo banu Aamir ki eik shaakh bani Kilaab mein sey they aur Zaid Taai jo banu Tey ki eik shaakh banu nabhaan sey they. is par Quraish key (nau muslim) sardar naraz ho gaey aur kehney lagey : aap Najad key (nau muslim) sardaron ko dey rahey hain aur hamein mehroom rakh rahey hain (halanke hum aap key qaribi hain?) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey aisa is liye kiya hai ke un ki taaleef qalb karun (dil moh lene ke liye). eik shakhs aaya jiski dadhi ghani, rukhsaar ubhrey huye, aankhen gehri, maathaa aagey ko badha huwa aur sar mundaa huwa tha, wo kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! Allah sey dar. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main Allah Taala ka nafarman hun to Allah Taala ka farman-bardar kon hoga? Allah Taala to mujhey zamin walon (tamam insanon jinnon) par ameen janta hai aur tum mujhey ameen nahin jantey. phir wo shakhs peeth pher kar chala gaya. haazirin mein sey eik shakhs ney aap sey uskey qatl ki ijazat talab ki. ehale ilm ka khayal hai ke wo Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (ijazat to na di magar) farmaya : yaqinan uski nasal (qabiley) main aisey log hongey jo Quran padhengey magar wo unkey halaq sey nichey nahin utreyga. wo musalmanon ko qatl kerengey aur but paraston ko chhod dengey (unhein kuchh nahin kahengey). wo Islam sey yun nikal jaeyngey jaisey tez teer apney nishaaney ko phaad kar nikal jata hai. wallah ! agar mainey in ko pa liya to unhein qome-Aad ki tarah qatl karunga."
2580,"Hazrat Qabeesa bin Makhaariq (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, unhoney kaha : mainey koi tawaan (jurmaana) apney zimmey ley liya, phir main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur aap sey uski (adaegi mein taawun ki) baabat sawal kiya to aap ney farmaya : maangna sirf teen qisam key logon key liye jayez hai. un mein sey eik wo shakhs hai jisney kisi qom mein (suleh karwaaney key liye) koi tawaan (jurmaana) apney zimmey ley liya. wo is silsiley mein logon sey madad mang sakta hai. yahan tak ke tawaan utaar dey aur phir maangney sey ruk jaey."
2581,"Hazrat Qabeesa bin Makhaariq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey eik maali bojh apney zimmey ley liya, phir uski (adaegi mein taawun ki) baabat sawal karney ke liye main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa. aap ney farmaya : Qabeesa ! hamarey paas thehro. koi sadqa aa gaya to tumhein deney ka hukm dengey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Qabeesa ! Zakat maangna sirf teen aadmiyon key liye jayez hai : eik to wo shakhs jisney (jhagda nimtaaney key liye) koi (maali) bojh apney zimmey ley liya, to uskey liye Zakat aur sadqaat lena jayez hai, yahan tak ke uski zarurat puri ho jaey. aur doosra wo shakhs jis par koi naa-gahaani aafat aa gaee jisney us ka maal khatam kar diya. uskey liye bhi maangna jayez hai yahan tak ke us ka guzaaraa honey lagey, phir wo maangney sey ruk jaey. aur teesra wo shakhs jisey faaqon ki nobat aa gaee yahan tak ke uski qom key teen samajh daar (moatabar) aadmi gawahi den ke waqaee falan shakhs faaqa-zada hai, to uskey liye bhi maangna jayez hai yahan tak ke wo zindagi guzarney key qabil ho jaey. aey Qabeesa ! in halaat key ilawa maangna haram hai aur maangney wala haram khata hai."
2582,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma huye aur hum aap key ird-gird beth gaey. aap ney farmaya : mujhey tumharey barey mein is baat ka dar hai ke merey baad tumharey liye duniya ki zeb aur zeenat aam kar di jaeygi. eik aadmi ney arz kiya : kya khair bhi shar ko lata hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. us shakhs sey kaha gaya ke kya baat hai ke to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey baat kar raha hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tujh sey baat nahin kar rahey hain? phir hamein andaza huwa ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par ""wahi"" utar rahi hai. haalate-wahi khatam hui to aap ney paseena poonchhtey huye farmaya : kya wo shakhs mojud hai jisney puchha tha? waaqaee khair shar ko nahin lata magar mausame-bahar ka ugaya huwa sabza bhi kabhi janwer ko maar deta hai ya qaribul-maut kar deta hai. magar wo janwer jo chaara khaye yahan tak ke jab uski kokhein ubhar jaaeyn (us ka pet bhar jaey) to wo aen suraj ki taraf munh kar key beth jaey (jugaali kerey) gobar kerey, peshab kerey. phir (jab bhook lagey to) charney lagey. yaqinan ye maal sabz (hara) aur mitha hai. bilashuba ye momin ka achchhaa sathi hai ba-sharte-ke wo us sey yatim, miskeen aur musafir ko dey. jo shakhs us maal ko nahaq leta hai, wo us (bimar) shakhs ki tarah hai jo khata rehta hai, magar sair nahin hota. aur ye maal qiyamat key din us shakhs key khilaf gawahi dega."
2583,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : miskeen aadmi ko sadqa dena sirf sadqa hai jabkey qurbat daar ko sadqa dena sadqa bhi hai aur sila-rehmi bhi."
2584,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Hazrat Zainab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik dafa) aurton sey farmaya : sadqa karo chahey zewrat hi sey ho. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) taqriban khaali haath they. un ki biwi Zainab un sey kehney lagin : kya is baat ki gunjaaish hai ke main apna sadqa aap ko aur apney bhai key yatim bachon ko dey dun? Hazrat Abdullah kehney lagey : is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochho. wo kehti hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghar aai to aap key darwazey par eik Ansari aurat khadi thi. us ka naam bhi Zainab tha. us ka matloob bhi wohi tha jo mera tha. itney mein Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) nikley. hamney un sey arz kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jaeyn aur aap sey ye masla poochhen lekin aap ko ye na batana ke hum kon hain? wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaey (aur puchha) to aap ney farmaya : wo kon aurten hain? unhoney kaha : Zainab, aap ney farmaya : kon si Zainab? unhoney arz kiya : eik Zainab to Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi aur dusri Zainab Ansari aurat hai. aap ney farmaya : haan ! unhein do ajr milengey : qurbat (sila-rehmi) ka ajr aur sadqey ka ajr."
2585,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey mazkur hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey eik shakhs lakdiyon ka gathaa apni peeth par uthaey aur usey farokht karey (aur munaaafa hasil kerey) ye us baat sey behtar hai ke wo kisi aadmi sey maangey. wo usey kuchh dey ya na dey.
2586,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi hamesha maangta rehta hai yahan tak ke wo qiyamat key din is haal mein (logon key samney) aayega ke uskey chehrey mein gosht ka tukda bhi na hoga."
2587,Hazrat Aaid bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap sey kuchh maangney laga. aap ney usey dey diya. jab us ney apna paon darwazey ki dehleez par rakha to aap ney farmaya : agar tum maangney ki qabaahat (ya saza aur gunah) jaan lo to tum mein sey koi kisi key paas kuchh bhi maangney na jaey.
2588,ibne Faraasi sey riwayat hai ke merey walid Hazrat Faraasi (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main kisi sey kuchh mang liya karun? aap ney farmaya : nahin. aur agar tujhey majbooran maangna padey to nek logon sey mang.
2589,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke kuchh Ansaar ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (maal) manga. aap ney unhein ata kiya. unhoney phir manga. aap ney phir diya yahan tak ke jab aap key paas jo kuchh tha khatam ho gaya, to aap ney farmaya : merey paas jo bhi maal hoga, main wo tum sey chhupa kar na rakhunga. aur jo shakhs sawal sey perhez kerega, Allah Taala usey maangney sey mehfooz rakheyga. aur jo shakhs sabr kerega, Allah Taala usey sabir banaeyga. aur kisi shakhs ko sabr sey ziyada achchha aur wasee Atiya nahin diya gaya."
2590,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum mein sey eik Shakhs apni rassi pakdey aur apni pusht par lakdiyon ka gathaa laad kar laye (aur usey bech kar guzaaraa kerey) us baat sey kahin ziyada behtar hai ke wo kisi aisey aadmi key paas jaey jisey Allah Taala ney apney Fazal sey nawaz rakha hai aur us sey ja kar maangey, phir wo usey dey ya na dey."
2591,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mujhey eik baat ki zamanat dey dey, uskey liye jannat hai. aur wo baat ye hai ke wo kisi insan sey kuchh na maangeyga."
2592,"Hazrat Qabeesa bin Makhaariq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : maangna sirf teen aadmiyon key liye jayez hai : eik wo shakhs jis key maal par koi naa-gahaani aafat aa gaee to wo mang sakta hai yahan tak ke guzaaraa ho sakey, phir wo maangney sey baaz aa jaey. aur eik wo shakhs jisney koi tawaan (jurmaana) apney zimmey ley liya, wo mang sakta hai yahan tak ke wo tawaan ada kerey. phir wo maangney sey baaz aa jaey. aur eik wo shakhs jiski qom key teen samajh-daar (moazziz) ashkhaas Allah Taala key naam ki qism uthaeyn ke falan shakhs (ki haalat ye ho gaee hai ke us) key liye maangna halal ho gaya hai. to wo mang sakta hai yahan tak ke munasib guzaaraa kar sakey, phir wo maangney sey baaz aa jaey. un teen Suraton key ilawa maangna haram hai."
2593,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs maangey, halanke uskey paas itna maal hai jo usey kifaayat kar sakta hai, to qiyamat key din us ka chehra nocha huwa hoga. puchha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kitna maal eik shakhs ko kifaayat kar sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : pachas dirham ya us (key barabar) maaliyat ka sona. Yahya kehtey hain ke Sufiyan Sooraa ney kaha, mainey Zubaida ko suna wo usey Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid sey bayan kar rahey they."
2594,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : israr key sath (chimat kar) na manga karo. tum mein sey jo shakhs bhi mujh sey kuchh maangeyga jabkey main usey dena pasand na karun (aur wo mujhey tang kar key kuchh maal ley jaey) to uskey liye is mein barkat na hogi jo main usey dunga."
2595,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi chaalis dirham honey key bawajud maangey to wo israr key sath (chimat kar) maangney wala hai."
2596,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mujhey meri walida ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bheja. main aap key paas aa kar beth gaya. aap ney apna chehra anwar meri taraf farmaya : jo shakhs apney aap ko mustaghni (beniyaaz) zahir kerey. Allah Taala usey ghani farma deta hai. aur jo shakhs sawal sey perhez kerey. Allah Taala usey sawal sey bacha leta hai. aur jo shakhs sirf kifaayat ka Talib ho, Allah Taala usey kifaayat farmata hai. aur jo shakhs eik auqiya (chaalis dirham) ki maaliyat wali chiz key hotey huye maangey to goya wo israr key sath mang raha hai. (Abu-Saeed ney farmaya : ) mainey (dil mein) kaha ke meri oontni yaaqoota eik oqiye sey ziyada qeemti hai, lihaza mein aap sey maangey baghair wapis aa gaya."
2597,"banu-Asad key eik shakhs sey riwayat hai ke main aur meri biwi Baqee al gharqad mein farokash huye (aaye) to mujhey meri biwi kehney lagi : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jao aur khaney ki koi chiz mang lao. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya to mainey aap key paas eik aur aadmi betha paya jo aap sey mang raha tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : merey paas koi aisi chiz nahin jo main tujhey dey sakun. wo aadmi ghussey ki haalat mein uth kar chala gaya aur kehney laga : meri zindagi ki qism ! jis ko aap ki marzi ho, dey detey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye mujh par is liye naraz hai ke merey paas koi aisi chiz nahin jo main usey dey sakun (yaad rakho ! ) tum mein sey jis shakhs ney eik auqiya ya uskey masaawi (barabar) dolat ki chiz ka Malik honey key bawajud manga to goya us ney israr key sath manga (jo ke mazmoom hai). Asadi shakhs ney kaha ke mainey (apney dil mein) kaha : hamari doodh wali oontni yaqinan eik oqiye sey badh kar hai. aur auqiya chaalis dirham ka hota hai. to main maangey baghair uth aaya. kuchh der baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas kuchh jau aur kishmish aa gaee. aap ney wo hum mein taqseem farma diye yahan tak ke Allah Taala ney hamein ghani kar diya."
2598,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Zakat aur sadqaat kisi maal daar shakhs ya kisi taqatwar tandurust shakhs key liye jayez nahin."
2599,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Adi bin Khiyaar sey riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ney mujh sey bayan kiya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Zakat aur sadqaat maangney aaye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein ghor sey dekha to unhein mota taza paya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tum majbur karo to main tumhen dey deta hun lekin maal-daar, kama sakney waley taqatwar shakhs ka Zakat mein koi hissa nahin."
2600,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba maangna kharaashein hain. aadmi apney chehrey ko unkey zariey sey nochta hai. ab jo chahey apna chehra nauchey aur jo chahey rehney dey. siwaey iske ke koi shakhs sahibe-iqtidar sey maangey ya aisi chiz maangey jis key baghair chaara na ho."
2601,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maangna to apney aap ko zakhmi karna hai. is tareeqey sey aadmi apney chehrey ko nochta hai, magar ye ke haakim sey maangey ya aisi chiz maangey jis key baghair chaara na ho."
2602,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey manga, aap ney dey diya. mainey phir manga, aap ney phir dey diya, mainey phir manga, aap ney phir diya magar sath hi farmaya : aey Hakim ! bilashuba ye maal sabz (hara) aur sheereen hai. jo shakhs isey nafs ki pakizgi key sath lega, uskey liye is mein barkat hogi. aur jo isey lalach aur tamaa (lalach) key sath lega, uskey liye is mein barkat na hogi. aur wo us shakhs ki tarah hoga jo khata hai lekin sair nahin hota. aur ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey behtar hai."
2603,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (maal) manga, aap ney dey diya. mainey phir manga, aap ney phir dey diya. mainey phir manga, aap ney phir diya. aur farmaya : aey Hakim ! bilashuba ye maal sabz (hara) aur sheereen hai. jo shakhs isey qanaa'at qalb (dil ke itminaan aur sabr) key sath lega, uskey liye is mein barkat hogi. aur jo shakhs isey dili tamaa (lalach) aur lalach key sath lega, uskey liye is mein barkat na hogi. aur wo us shakhs ki tarah hoga jo khata hai magar sair nahin hota. aur ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey (har surat mein) behtar hai."
2604,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kuchh manga. aap ney diya. mainey phir manga, aap ney phir diya. phir farmaya : aey Hakim ! bilashuba ye maal sheereen (chiz ki tarah achchha lagta) hai lekin jo shakhs isey be-niyazi sey hasil kerega, uskey liye is mein barkat hogi. aur jo lalach key sath hasil kerega, uskey liye is mein barkat na hogi. aur wo us shakhs ki tarah hoga jo khata hai magar sair nahin hota. aur ooper wala haath nichey waley haath sey behtar hai. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai ! main aap (key is farman) key baad kabhi kisi sey kuchh na lunga yahan tak ke main duniya chhod jaun."
2605,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaidi Maaliki sey manqul hai ke mujhey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney sadqa aur Zakat jama karney par muqarrar farmaya. jab main is zimmey-daari sey farigh huwa aur mainey (jama shuda) maal un ki khidmat mein pesh kiya to aap ney mujhey meri khidmat ka moawza deney ka hukm jari farmaya. mainey kaha : mainey ye kaam Allah Taala ki raza-mandi key liye kiya hai. is ka moawza mujhey Allah Taala hi dega. aap ney farmaya : jo main tumhein dey raha hun, ley lo. mainey bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein (aisi hi) khidmat sar anjam di thi aur mainey bhi aap sey teri tarah hi kaha tha to mujh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tujhey koi chiz terey maangey baghair miley to (usey ley ley aur) kha. aur (chahey to) sadqa kar dey."
2606,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sa'di sey riwayat hai ke main ilaaqaey-Shaam sey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. unhoney farmaya : mujhey bataya gaya hai ke tum musalmanon key kaam (sarkari khidmaat) sar anjam detey ho aur phir jab tumhen moawza diya jata hai to tum qubul nahin kartey? mainey arz kiya : ji haan ! merey paas bahut sey ghodey aur ghulam hain. main maal-daar hun aur chahta hun ke meri tankhwaah musalmanon par sadqa ho jaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein) mainey bhi aisa hi karna chah tha jis tarah tu ney karna chah hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey maal waghera (basurat moawza) ata farmatey to main keh deta ke ye kisi aisey shakhs ko dey dijiye jo mujh sey ziyada zarurat mand ho. eik dafa aap ney mujhey kuchh maal ata farmaya to mainey arz kiya ke ye aisey shakhs ko dey den jo mujh sey ziyada mohtaj ho, to aap ney farmaya : jo maal tujhey Allah Taala terey maangey aur lalach aur tamaa (lalach) key baghair dey, usey ley liya kar, phir chahey to apney paas rakh, chahey sadqa kar dey. aur jo maal is tarah apney aap na miley uskey peechhey apney aap ko na laga."
2607,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sa'di ney bataya ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-khilaafat mein unkey paas hazir huwa to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey farmaya : kya ye baat durust hai ke tum sarkari kaam kartey ho aur jab tumhein khidmat ka haq diya jata hai to tum wapis kar detey ho? mainey kaha : ji haan. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : tumhara maqsad kya hota hai? mainey kaha : merey paas bahut sey ghodey aur ghulam hain. main maal-daar hun. (merey paas Allah Taala ka diya bahut kuchh hai). main chahta hun ke meri tankhwaah musalmanon par sadqa ho jaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aisey na kiya karo. mainey bhi (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein) aisa hi karna chah tha jis tarah tu ney karna chaha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey koi Atiya waghera detey to main keh deta ke ye kisi aisey shakhs ko dey dijiye jisey uski mujh sey ziyada zarurat ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ley liya kar, phir ji chahey to rakh ley, nahin to sadqa kar diya kar. is qisam ka maal jo terey paas baghair teri tamaa (lalach) (lalach) aur khahish key aaye, wo ley liya kar aur jo is tarah na miley uskey peechhey apney aap ko na laga."
2608,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sa'di ney khabar di ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-hukoomat mein aap key paas aaya to aap farmaney lagey : mujhey pataa chala hai ke to logon ki khidmaat sar anjam deta hai lekin jab tujhey tankhwaah di jati hai to to usey napasand karta hai? mainey kaha : haan ! (aisey hi hai). to unhoney farmaya : tumhara maqsad kya hota hai? mainey kaha : merey paas bahut sey ghodey aur ghulam hain aur main maal-daar hun (achchha guzaaraa kar raha hun). main chahta hun ke meri tankhwaah musalmanon par sadqa ho jaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya aisey na kar. mainey bhi aisa hi karna chaha tha jis tarah tu ney karna chah hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey tankhwaah waghera detey to main keh deta ke ye kisi ziyada hajat mand ko dey dijiye, yahan tak ke eik dafa aap ney mujhey kuchh maal diya. mainey (hasabe-aadat) keh diya ke ye mujh sey ziyada mohtaj ko dey dijiye. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmaney lagey : ley ley, phir rakh ya sadqa kar. is qisam ka maal terey paas aaye jabkey tujhey na lalach ho aur na tu ney manga ho to wo ley liya kar aur jo khud ba-khud na miley, uskey peechhey apney aap ko na laga."
2609,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huye suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey koi Atiya inayat farmatey to main keh diya karta tha ke ye kisi aisey shakhs ko dey dijiye jisey mujh sey ziyada is ki zarurat ho, yahan tak ke eik dafa aap ney mujhey kuchh maal diya to mainey keh diya : kisi aisey shakhs ko dey dijiye jo mujh sey ziyada faqir hai. aap ney farmaya : ley ley. isey istimal bhi kar aur sadqa bhi kar. ye maal agar terey paas khud ba-khud aaye, tujhey na to is ki tamaa (lalach) (laalach) ho aur na tu ney manga ho to usey ley liya kar aur jo apney aap na miley, uskey peechhey apney aap ko na laga."
2610,"Hazrat Abdul-Muttalib bin Rabeea bin Haris bin Abdul-Muttalib Raziallahu anhum ney bataya ke merey walid Rabeea bin Haris ney mujhey aur Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jao aur aap sey arz karo ke hamein bhi sadqaat ikhattey karney ki khidmat par muqarrar farmaeyn. abhi hum ye baaten kar hi rahey they ke Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye aur farmaney lagey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tum mein sey kisi ko sadqaat par muqarrar nahin farmaeyngey. main aur Fazal bin Abbas phir bhi chal padey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunch kar arz kiya to aap ney farmaya : ye Zakat aur sadqaat logon ka mail kuchail hain, is liye ye Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye halal nahin."
2611,Hazrat Shoba bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Abu-Ayaas Muawiya bin Qurra sey puchha : kya tum ney Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi qom ka bhaanjaa bhi us qom mein shamil hai? unhoney kaha : haan.
2612,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi qom ka bhaanjaa bhi un mein sey hi hai."
2613,Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney banu Makhzoom key eik shakhs ko sadqaat jama karney par muqarrar farmaya. Abu-Raafea' (yani main) ney bhi uskey sath janey ki khahish ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sadqaat hamarey liye halal nahin aur kisi khandan ka azad karda ghulam bhi un mein shamil hai.
2614,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada bayan kartey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas koi chiz laee jati to aap uskey barey mein poochhtey ke ye tohfa hai ya sadqa? agar kaha jata : sadqa hai, to aap nahin khatey they aur agar kaha jata hai : tohfa hai, to aap tanaawul farma letey they."
2615,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke mainey irada kiya ke Barira (Raziallahu anha) ko kharid kar azad kar dun lekin uskey malikon ney uskey walaa ki shart laga li. mainey ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : kharid kar azad kar dey. walaa usi ka haq hai jo azad kerey. (isi tarah) jab wo azad hui to usey (khawind key paas rehney ya na rehney ka) ikhtiyar diya gaya. (isi tarah) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gosht laya gaya aur bataya gaya ke ye us (gosht) main sey hai jo Barira (Raziallahu anha) par sadqa kiya gaya hai. aap ney farmaya : wo uskey liye sadqa hai, hamarey liye hadiya (tohfa) hai. (yaad rahey ke) Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) ka khawind azad tha."
2616,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey eik ghodaa Allah Taala key raastey (jihad) main kisi (Mujahid) ko diya. us ney ghodey (ki khatir tawaazeh na ki aur us) ko zaya (kamzor) kar diya. mera irada huwa ke us sey dobara kharid lun. mera khayal tha wo sastaa hi bech dega. mainey is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : to usey mat kharid. chahey wo eik dirham hi ka tujhey dey kyonkey jo shakhs apney sadqey ko (kisi bhi surat mein) wapis leta hai, wo us kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai chaatta hai."
2617,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney eik ghodaa Allah ke raastey mein sadqa kiya, phir unhein pataa chala ke wo ghodaa farokht ho raha hai to unhoney khud hi khareedney ka irada kar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney kiye huye sadqey (ki wapsi) ka khayal bhi na kar."
2618,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik ghodaa Allah Taala key raastey mein sadqa kiya. kuchh arsey key baad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney dekha ke wo ghodaa farokht kiya ja raha hai to unhoney irada farmaya ke main hi usey kharid lun, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur is barey mein aap sey mashwara talab kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apna kiya huwa sadqa dobara na ley."
2619,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Makka Mukarrama key governer) Hazrat Itaab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya tha ke angooron ki fasal ka andaza laga kar un ki Zakat kishmish ki surat mein ada ki jaey jis tarah khajuron ki Zakat khushk khajuron (chhuwaaron) ki surat mein ada ki jati hai.
